text: María Teresa Jiménez Esquivel (born 25 May 1984 in Valle de Bravo, State of Mexico) is a Mexican politician and current governor of Aguascalientes, member of the National Action Party and former deputy of the Chamber of Deputies, she was Municipal President of Aguascalientes. == References == Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Mexico (state) Category:People from Aguascalientes Category:Mexican mayors
title: María Teresa Jiménez Esquivel
